1.1.name: wordpress/facebook-open-graph-meta
1.1.description: Facebook Open Graph Meta is a wordpress plugin that will help you to add open graph protocol meta data in your blog. When your visitors share or like your blog post or page the shared post will show on his facebook wall in a nice way. So that his friends get inspire to checkout the shared post.
